Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被忽視的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被捉弄的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.61,0:00:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無家可歸  漫無目的地走在路上時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳心的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其被人扯碎校服  撕破心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如直接剁碎自己的軀體  來得痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛快得多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.65,0:00:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.68,0:00:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把你從Black  Rock  Shooter中拯救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.08,0:00:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  萬一無法實現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.29,0:01:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓我親手把真透…不  這不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯獨這點一定要避免
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.64,0:01:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼意思  優
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.52,0:01:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.54,0:01:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優  優
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.47,0:01:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  優  優
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回答我  優
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是優的精神體
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要精神體消失  現在優所承受的痛苦也會隨即消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘卻痛苦的優  就不會在這裡駐足不前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:02:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  住手  我不想回到現實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.32,0:02:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.63,0:02:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.33,0:02:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想  優是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漆黑無光  道路即將崩毀…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是Black  Rock  Shooter的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  是你的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷的滋味如何  Black  Rock  Shooter
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strength
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  為什麼要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是消失了  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:04:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不得不回到現實了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好孤單  我明明已經無家可歸了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤單？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透想要拯救我  拯救優的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我過去把一切都推給了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的痛苦  煩惱  迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好  我們就是為此而生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對！我不想傷害任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優  黃泉  甚至是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.59,0:04:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我想受傷  並且自己承受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想受傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:05:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  想要受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不受傷就無法看到各種各樣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我想看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢地去直視
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容的橙色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒的粉紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼淚的藍色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困惑的紫色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懊惱的紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是伴隨著痛苦的顏色  我也想親眼看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不需要毫無痛楚的自愈的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想好好受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就來傷害你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我們不同  你們的傷不可能輕易痊癒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.86,0:05:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不用那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要  我才不用這些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不像話了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想傷害他人  卻想自己受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不像話了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這是傷害他人的痛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不傷害別人  只想自己受傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點程度就動彈不能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要傷害別人  我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繽紛小鳥死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此還是死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顏色的記憶死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顏色——
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是藍天！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我是為了看到繽紛的顏色而飛翔
